query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, a.id as anamnesis_id, a.mainGoal, a.experienceLevel, a.trainingFrequency 
FROM students s 
LEFT JOIN anamneses a ON s.id = a.studentId 
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Laura%' 
LIMIT 5;
